  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed rear dormer roof extension, by reason of its inappropriate size, scale and detailed design, massing, bulk and form would introduce a dominant and visually discordant feature to the roof slope that fails to be subordinate or sympathetic to the character and appearance of the host property, the terrace and locality. The proposal would disrupt a predominately unbroken roofline and would be clearly visible from the surrounding private realm.  The proposed development would be contrary to the NPPF (2021), policy D3 of the London Plan (2021), policy CS8 of the Islington Core Strategy (2011), policy DM2.1 of the Islington Development Management document (2013) & Islington's Urban Design Guidance."
